        <h4>This is an easy oatmeal-banana cookie recipie</h4>
        <br /><br />
        <p class="aligncenter">
            Ingredients: <br />
            Oatmeal (2 cups) <br />
            Banana (1 ripe)<br />
            <br /> Optional Toppings:
            <br />
            Chocolate Chips<br />
            Peanut Butter<br />
            Cinnamon<br />
            <br /><br />
            How to prepare the cookies<br />
            Preheat the oven to 350 degrees fahrenheit<br />
            Mix together the oatmeal and banana with a fork and add the toppings of choice when fully combined<br />
            Portion cookies on a parchment paper lined baking sheet<br />
            Bake cookies for 10-12 minutes and enjoy!<br /><br /><br />

            <img src="/images/food/cookies.jpg" alt="Oatmeal cookies!" width="360" height="640" />
